<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="break-n">break <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /breɪk/    美 /breɪk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>休息；暂停；广告时间：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>have / take a short break</strong>
稍作休息/休息一小会儿</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>coffee / lunch break</strong>
喝咖啡的/午餐休息时间</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>More news after the break. 
广告之后继续报道新闻。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>短暂的假期；休假：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the Christmas / summer break
圣诞节假期/暑假</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>裂口；缺口：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The sun shone through a break in the clouds. 
阳光透过云层的缝隙照下来。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>天亮；拂晓：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>at the break of day / at daybreak
拂晓时分</p></div></div>